sourcesContent:
import React from 'react';
import { 
  Container, 
  Row, 
  Col, 
  Card, 
  CardBody, 
  CardTitle, 
  CardText, 
  ListGroup, 
  ListGroupItem,
  Badge
} from 'reactstrap';

const HomePage = () => {
  return (
    <Container className="mt-4">
      <Row>
        <Col md="10" className="mx-auto">
          <Card className="shadow-lg border-0">
            <CardBody>
              <CardTitle tag="h2" className="text-center mb-4 text-primary">
                Fundamentos de Programación Web
              </CardTitle>
              
              <Row>
                <Col md="6">
                  <Card className="mb-4 border-0 bg-light">
                    <CardBody>
                      <CardTitle tag="h5" className="text-dark">
                        Información del Estudiante
                      </CardTitle>
                      <ListGroup flush>
                        <ListGroupItem className="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                          Nombre
                          <Badge color="primary" pill>Pablo Alvarado Umaña</Badge>
                        </ListGroupItem>
                      </ListGroup>
                    </CardBody>
                  </Card>
                </Col>
                
                <Col md="6">
                  <Card className="mb-4 border-0 bg-light">
                    <CardBody>
                      <CardTitle tag="h5" className="text-dark">
                        Detalles del Curso
                      </CardTitle>
                      <ListGroup flush>
                        <ListGroupItem className="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                          Periodo
                          <Badge color="success" pill>CICLO I 2025</Badge>
                        </ListGroupItem>
                        <ListGroupItem className="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                          NRC
                          <Badge color="info" pill>41663</Badge>
                        </ListGroupItem>
                        <ListGroupItem className="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                          Número de Curso
                          <Badge color="warning" pill>428O</Badge>
                        </ListGroupItem>
                      </ListGroup>
                    </CardBody>
                  </Card>
                </Col>
              </Row>

              <Row>
                <Col>
                  <Card className="bg-light border-0">
                    <CardBody>
                      <CardTitle tag="h5" className="text-dark">
                        Información Adicional
                      </CardTitle>
                      <ListGroup flush>
                        <ListGroupItem className="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                          Campus
                          <Badge color="secondary" pill>Sede Interuniversit. Alajuela</Badge>
                        </ListGroupItem>
                        <ListGroupItem className="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                          Tipo de Horario
                          <Badge color="primary" outline pill>Teoría y laboratorio</Badge>
                        </ListGroupItem>
                        <ListGroupItem className="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                          Método Educativo
                          <Badge color="success" outline pill>Presencial</Badge>
                        </ListGroupItem>
                        <ListGroupItem className="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                          Instructor
                          <Badge color="info" pill>Juan Ramos Peñaranda</Badge>
                        </ListGroupItem>
                        <ListGroupItem className="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                          Horas Crédito
                          <Badge color="warning" pill>3</Badge>
                        </ListGroupItem>
                        <ListGroupItem className="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                          Modo de Calificación
                          <Badge color="dark" pill>Calificación estándar</Badge>
                        </ListGroupItem>
                      </ListGroup>
                    </CardBody>
                  </Card>
                </Col>
              </Row>
            </CardBody>
          </Card>
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default HomePage;
